      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation with plenty of potential for the right buyer. A practical choice for someone seeking an inexpensive daily driver, first car, or project opportunity, it delivers strong value at an accessible price point. Sold as-is and represented honestly, this is a straightforward chance to get into a vehicle without overspending.",
