    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little runabout that could make a great starter, project, or budget commuter. It\u2019s priced with its condition in mind and offers a lot of value for someone who doesn\u2019t mind a few cosmetic and age-related quirks. If you want something affordable and straightforward, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 3950.0,
