      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Strong-running project car with a willing powertrain, responsive steering, and a chassis that still feels eager on the road. Not a showpiece, but it has the kind of honest driver character enthusiasts appreciate\u2014good bones, usable torque, and plenty of potential for a budget build, commuter, or weekend fixer-upper. A practical buy for someone who wants an affordable entry point and doesn\u2019t mind cosmetic flaws or finishing touches.",
