    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough for someone who appreciates character, this car has the kind of presence that still turns heads in a parking lot and the kind of story that makes every drive feel a little more interesting. It\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly way to get behind the wheel of something with real personality\u2014perfect for a hands-on owner, a first project, or anyone looking for dependable transportation with soul and potential. If you\u2019ve been searching for an affordable ride with charm, grit, and room to make it your own, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
